trans-unit.source: Specifies the return value of a <xref href="System.ServiceProcess.Design.ServiceInstallerDialog"></xref> form.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o valor de retorno de um <xref href="System.ServiceProcess.Design.ServiceInstallerDialog"> </xref> formulário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceProcess.Design.ServiceInstallerDialog.Result%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property uses this enumeration to indicate the user response to the dialog box.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceProcess.Design.ServiceInstallerDialog.Result%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade usa esta enumeração para indicar a resposta do usuário à caixa de diálogo.</xref:System.ServiceProcess.Design.ServiceInstallerDialog.Result%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The dialog return value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_Canceled" name="Canceled" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A caixa de diálogo valor de retorno é <xref uid="langword_csharp_Canceled" name="Canceled" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This value typically indicates that the user canceled out of the dialog without setting the account fields.
trans-unit.target: Esse valor normalmente indica que o usuário cancelou fora da caixa de diálogo sem definir os campos de conta.

trans-unit.source: The dialog return value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_OK" name="OK" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A caixa de diálogo valor de retorno é <xref uid="langword_csharp_OK" name="OK" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This value typically indicates that the user confirmed the account properties and pressed the <xref uid="langword_csharp_OK" name="OK" href=""></xref> button to close the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Esse valor normalmente indica que o usuário confirmar as propriedades da conta e pressionado o <xref uid="langword_csharp_OK" name="OK" href=""> </xref> para fechar a caixa de diálogo.

trans-unit.source: Install the service with a system account rather than a user account.
trans-unit.target: Instale o serviço com uma conta do sistema em vez de uma conta de usuário.

trans-unit.source: This value typically indicates that the dialog was not displayed to the user.
trans-unit.target: Esse valor normalmente indica que a caixa de diálogo não foi exibida ao usuário.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.ServiceProcess.ServiceProcessInstaller.Account%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to something other than <xref uid="langword_csharp_User" name="User" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.ServiceProcess.ServiceProcessInstaller.Account%2A?displayProperty=fullName> propriedade é definida como algo diferente de <xref uid="langword_csharp_User" name="User" href=""> </xref>.
